Contract Title: Partnership Agreement between Skylandia Solutions LLC and TerraNova Consortium, Ltd.
Parties Involved: Skylandia Solutions LLC & TerraNova Consortium, Ltd.
Confidentiality Clause: The parties agree to maintain all information exchanged under this Contract as strictly confidential, disclosing such only to personnel or service providers who need to know such information for carrying out obligations under the Contract.
Amendment Clause: Any amendments or modifications to this Contract must be executed in writing and signed by both parties.
